text.section:
Nothing in this section shall apply to the killing or injuring of a dog or cat:
In accordance with a license to hunt, fish, or trap;
For humane purposes;
For veterinary, agricultural, spaying or neutering, or cosmetic purposes;
For purposes relating to sporting activities including but not limited to training for organized dog or cat shows, or other animal shows in which a dog or a cat, or both, participate;
For bona fide animal research activities, using dogs or cats, of institutions of higher education; or a business entity registered with the United States Department of Agriculture under the Animal Welfare Act or subject to other federal laws governing animal research;
In defense of self or another person against an aggressive or diseased dog or cat;
In defense of a domestic animal against an aggressive or diseased dog or cat;
For animal or pest control; or
For any other purpose authorized by law.
